| **ProfilePostCards Pattern** | `useInfiniteQuery` with `created_at` ISO timestamp cursor, page size 5, IntersectionObserver sentinel on `.in-view-container` |
| **getUserStories Backend** | ❌ NO pagination - returns full array, needs modification |
| **getStories Backend** | ✅ Full support - `limit` (1-20) + `before` cursor pagination |
